{"3257270": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Haunted by Femboy", "steam_appid": 3257270, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257270/extras/315e7844a3787d06bf80f3326d208ef6.avif?t=1763017415\" width=569 height=352 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257270/extras/4985cd6c74afad5371b9ec72fb20ad75.avif?t=1763017415\" width=569 height=352 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《Haunted by Femboy》中，你意外地從疏遠的父親那裡繼承了一座神秘的豪宅。在探索新家時，你發現了一本名為「Bussy-Nomicon」的古老詛咒之書，並不小心召喚出了奎恩（Quinn）——一個被困在書中千年之久的妖嬈幽靈男娘。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >現在你們被永遠地聯繫在了一起，你能在應對這位新的幽靈夥伴的同時，揭開父親豪宅的祕密嗎？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257270/extras/5f5cf06fffbb720d33b1c6b8b7bf86ce.avif?t=1763017415\" width=568 height=217 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>遊戲特色：</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >根據遊戲過程中的決定和選擇，體驗多重結局。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >兩位可攻略的戀愛對象：奎恩和拉文（Quinn和Laverne）。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >所有主要劇情場景和事件均配備英語配音</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集品和小遊戲可以解鎖新場景</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >大多數香豔場景都有動態CG</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >支援多種語言</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完整的回放畫廊，可以解鎖並重溫所有已解鎖的場景</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >遊戲內可切換的NSFW和SFW模式，完美適合想要避免成人內容的實況主。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以及更多精彩內容。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay